      <p>Berklee's international campus in Valencia, Spain, offers master's degrees, study abroad opportunities, and summer programs, with an emphasis on global learning.</p><h5>Shortcuts</h5><p><a href="https://valencia.berklee.edu/academics/graduate-programs">Graduate degrees</a></p><p><a href="https://valencia.berklee.edu/undergraduate-programs/sa/study-abroad">Study abroad</a></p><p><a href="https://valencia.berklee.edu/academics/summer-programs">Summer programs</a></p>
    </div>
